---
import CtaButton from './../CtaButton.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="section about" aria-labelledby="about-title">
	<div class="section-inner">
		<p class="eyebrow">About Me</p>
		<div class="about-items">
			<article class="text-section" aria-labelledby="about-title">
				<h2 id="about-title">9+ years of experience</h2>
				<p>
					Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer interfejs
					tworzy proste, uzyteczne strony, narzedzia i systemy, ktore pomagaja firmom
					porzadkowac procesy, szybciej testowac pomysly i lepiej komunikowac wartosc
					uslug. Vivamus luctus, justo at facilisis gravida, arcu sem porttitor nisl,
					nec posuere mi sapien id lectus. Cos o tym ze duzo roznych problemow biznesowych
					rozwiazywalem, branze, Sassy etc. I ze frontend mi sprawia frajde bo to zarowno techniczne jak i artystyczne.
				</p>
			</article>

			<article class="text-section text-section-right" aria-labelledby="about-leadership-title">
				<h2 id="about-leadership-title">Leadership & Collaboration</h2>
				<p>
					Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, about how I have experience with leading
					groups of developers, working in cross-functional teams, and
					collaborating with stakeholders to deliver high-quality products as
					well as being the sole contractor. Coś ze I value communication.
				</p>
			</article>

			<article class="text-section" aria-labelledby="about-frontend-title">
				<h2 id="about-frontend-title">Versatile Frontend Expert</h2>
				<p>
					Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, React & Typescript mainly, but also Vue,
					Ionic, React Native, and other frameworks. Mention some more specific
					technologies and tools.
				</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>
	<CtaButton
		href="#projects"
		ariaLabel="Scroll to case studies section"
		label="View Projects"
		immediate
	/>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
		position: relative;
    padding: clamp(56px, 7vw, 112px) 0;
  }

  .section-inner {
    width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 0 60px 0;
  }

  .about {
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    background: #f8fafc; 
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .about-items {
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(64px, 10vh, 120px); 
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .text-section {
    max-width: 900px;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .text-section-right {
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #111827;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 3vw, 60px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .text-section p:last-child {
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    color: #334155;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .about-items {
      gap: 48px;
    }
    
    .text-section-right {
      margin-left: 0; 
    }
    
    .text-section {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .section-inner {
      width: min(100% - 28px, 1120px);
    }
  }
</style>
